metadata.plot: A journey across a dystopian future America, following a team of military-embedded journalists as they race against time to reach DC before rebel factions descend upon the White House.
metadata.overview: In the near future, a group of war journalists attempt to survive while reporting the truth as the United States stands on the brink of civil war.
metadata.title: Civil War

release_dates.note: South by Southwest Film & TV Festival
